<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="boil-v">boil <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɔɪl/    美 /bɔɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 沸腾；煮沸；煮：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>boiled water 
煮开过的水(可指凉开水)</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>boiling water 
正在沸腾的水</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Water <strong>boils at</strong> 100℃. 
水温达到100℃时沸腾。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>发怒；发火：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His rudeness made her <strong>boil with</strong> anger. 
他的无礼使她怒不可遏。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>100℃ is the temperature <strong><em>_</em></strong> which water will boil.   （2012 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. at  </p></div>